import {
  Image,
  Box,
  Flex,
  Heading,
  Text,
  Spacer,
  Button,
  Container,
  Grid,
  GridItem,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
const Static2 = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Box bg="#ccffff" borderLeftRadius="3xl" borderRightRadius="3xl">
        <Grid>
          <GridItem>
            <Image src="/images/salad.png" alt="Dan Abramov" />
          </GridItem>
          <></>
            <Text>
              <Heading marginBottom="10px" fontSize="25px">
                Delicious to your inbox
              </Heading>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur
              <Text>adipisicing elit. Doloremque eligendi, unde</Text>
              <input type="text" width="10px" value="enter your email" />
              <Button
                bg="black"
                color="white"
                marginTop="20px"
                border="2px solid black"
              >
                Subscribe
              </Button>
            </Text>
          <Flex>
            <Box>
              <Image src="/images/plate.png" alt="Dan Abramov" />
            </Box>
          </Flex>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </>
  );
};

export default Static2;
